text: Labor de Medina is a town in the municipality of San Martín de Hidalgo in the state of Jalisco, Mexico. It has a population of 863 inhabitants.Labor de Medina, San Martín Hidalgo, Jalisco ==References== ==External links== *Labor de Medina at PueblosAmerica.com Category:Populated places in Jalisco
